headline: Mitsubishi Electric to Transfer Shares of Insurance Subsidiary to Marsh Japan
summary: TOKYO, July 28, 2025--Mitsubishi Electric Corporation (TOKYO: 6503) announced today that it has concluded a share transfer agreement under which it will transfer shares of its Tokyo-based subsidiary Mitsubishi Electric Insurance Service Co., Ltd. to Marsh Japan, Inc. on November 4.
